Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:15.57,test,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H000000&\fr-5\pos(344.5,296)}屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:15.57,test,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H000000&\fr-5\pos(624.075,329.333)}hip
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:16.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:18.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:20.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:21.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.52,0:18:25.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,还是说想要我用身体告诉你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:30.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么啊 也太羞耻了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:31.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,春香…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:34.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,小春春怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:36.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an8}怎么了突然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:39.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an8}不要紧 好像还有气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:40.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an8}那是当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:41.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an8}更何况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.42,0:18:44.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an8}没事吧 还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:46.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an8}怎么就突然变成死啊活啊的问题了
